costfunc: computes a cost function for evaluating attractor reconstructions
author: Lucas C. Uzal

For details see:
L.C. Uzal, G.L. Grinblat and P.F. Verdes
"Optimal reconstruction of dynamical systems: A noise amplification approach"
(to be published)

This program is based on TISEAN - Nonlinear time series project
